26:34.801 --> 26:36.470
WHAT'S THE HARM?

26:36.512 --> 26:38.097
I LIKE THE WAY YOU DO BUSINESS.

26:38.138 --> 26:39.765
LOOKS LIKE THE BEAVERS' PITCHER

26:39.806 --> 26:41.350
IS CALLING A POWWOW

26:39.806 --> 26:41.350
