WELL, YOU KNOW,

28:00.179 --> 28:02.139
I CONSIDERED BELBRIDGE,

28:02.181 --> 28:04.642
BUT I LIKE THE INCENTIVES

28:02.181 --> 28:04.642
BEING OFFERED BY ANOTHER TOWN

28:04.682 --> 28:06.018
DOWN BY, UH, FALL RIVER.

28:06.059 --> 28:08.562
BY "INCENTIVES,"

28:06.059 --> 28:08.562
YOU MEAN CUT OF THE CONCESSION,

28:08.604 --> 28:10.439
PIECE OF THE CONSTRUCTION,

28:08.604 --> 28:10.439
A BUY-IN?

28:10.481 --> 28:12.191
AH, YOU ARE PRO-BUSINESS.

28:12.232 --> 28:13.733
ALL RIGHT, GIVE ME A NUMBER.

28:13.775 --> 28:16.570
